01:56:39,997 --> 01:56:42,344
<font face="Comic Sans MS">The thing is that
what I can't see</font>

1334
01:56:42,379 --> 01:56:45,692
<font face="Comic Sans MS">is that the... the..</font>

1335
01:56:45,727 --> 01:56:50,387
<font face="Comic Sans MS">...the box was bought here
in the shop.</font>

1336
01:56:50,421 --> 01:56:51,664
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Uh..</font>

1337
01:56:51,698 --> 01:56:54,598
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Well I buy all my shit here.</font>

1338
01:56:54,632 --> 01:56:56,738
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I have, for 20 years.</font>

1339
01:56:56,772 --> 01:57:01,294
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm in here
almost every other week.</font>

1340
01:57:01,329 --> 01:57:02,744
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What's wrong with you, Al?</font>

1341
01:57:04,125 --> 01:57:05,885
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm sorry,
I need to see a receipt.</font>

1342
01:57:06,817 --> 01:57:08,336
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Receipt?
- Yeah</font>

1343
01:57:08,370 --> 01:57:10,027
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, I don't have a fuckin'
receipt.</font>

1344
01:57:10,062 --> 01:57:12,340
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't ever recall getting a
receipt here.</font>

1345
01:57:12,374 --> 01:57:14,100
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Now I'm in a fucking hurry.</font>

1346
01:57:14,135 --> 01:57:16,551
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Let me buy a new box.</font>

1347
01:57:16,585 --> 01:57:17,966
<font face="Comic Sans MS">But this time make sure
it contains</font>

1348
01:57:18,001 --> 01:57:19,519
<font face="Comic Sans MS">full metal jacket bullets.</font>

1349
01:57:22,074 --> 01:57:26,216
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Okay, uh, c... can I just see
some ID first?</font>

1350
01:57:27,596 --> 01:57:28,943
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Don't fucking do this, Al.</font>

1351
01:57:28,977 --> 01:57:32,947
<font face="Comic Sans MS">The thing is, the... the law
requires that I have...</font>

1352
01:57:32,981 --> 01:57:34,155
<font face="Comic Sans MS">How about this..</font>

1353
01:57:34,189 --> 01:57:36,053
<font face="Comic Sans MS">No doubt about
your... your identity...</font>

1354
01:57:36,088 --> 01:57:38,262
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Sell me just one full metal
jacket bullet.</font>

1355
01:57:38,297 --> 01:57:40,747
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Can I, can I just ask..</font>

1356
01:57:43,026 --> 01:57:45,338
<font face="Comic Sans MS">...why just... one?</font>

1357
01:57:45,373 --> 01:57:47,375
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, that will be none of your
fuckin' business.</font>

1358
01:57:47,409 --> 01:57:49,204
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- That... that's right. I'm sor...
- Okay?</font>

1359
01:57:49,239 --> 01:57:52,069
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I do business here because you
don't ask stupid questions.</font>

1360
01:57:52,104 --> 01:57:56,280
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm... I'm sorry, Jack.
I'm... I'm sorry.</font>

1361
01:57:56,315 --> 01:57:59,594
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Shut it down, Al, go home, have a sandwich.
- Okay.</font>

1362
01:57:59,628 --> 01:58:00,948
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You've lost
your fucking mind, Al.</font>

1363
01:58:00,975 --> 01:58:02,838
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah. I'm sorry. I'm so..</font>

1364
01:58:04,047 --> 01:58:05,876
<font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Is it any wonder</font>



1366
01:58:10,053 --> 01:58:11,537
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Fuck you, Al!</font>

1367
01:58:13,988 --> 01:58:18,854
<font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Is it any wonder
you are too cool to fool?<i></font>




1370
01:58:27,070 --> 01:58:29,589
<font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Got to get a rain check
on pain<i></font>


1373
01:58:53,613 --> 01:58:55,684
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Al's gone totally bonkers.</font>

1374
01:58:55,719 --> 01:58:58,204
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I need a full metal jacket
cartridge.</font>

1375
01:59:00,034 --> 01:59:04,831
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Yesterday,
the police visited Al</font>

1376
01:59:04,866 --> 01:59:07,006
<font face="Comic Sans MS">and then me</font>

1377
01:59:07,041 --> 01:59:09,422
<font face="Comic Sans MS">with lights and sirens</font>

1378
01:59:09,457 --> 01:59:10,596
<font face="Comic Sans MS">to get you.</font>

1379
01:59:12,046 --> 01:59:13,978
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It's over now, Jack.</font>

1380
01:59:16,705 --> 01:59:17,982
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What's over?</font>

1381
01:59:19,363 --> 01:59:21,296
<font face="Comic Sans MS">They know what you've done.</font>

1382
01:59:25,024 --> 01:59:26,888
<font face="Comic Sans MS">We..</font>

1383
01:59:26,922 --> 01:59:28,959
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Alright, what have I done?</font>

1384
01:59:29,753 --> 01:59:31,099
<font face="Comic Sans MS">The robbery.</font>

1385
01:59:32,687 --> 01:59:34,033
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Robbery?</font>

1386
01:59:34,068 --> 01:59:36,691
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You guys better
fucking get it together.</font>

1387
01:59:36,725 --> 01:59:39,383
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I haven't robbed anybody.</font>

1388
01:59:39,418 --> 01:59:41,109
<font face="Comic Sans MS">This is ridiculous.</font>

1389
01:59:43,353 --> 01:59:46,080
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm gonna call the police, Jack.</font>

1390
01:59:47,874 --> 01:59:49,497
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Give me your gun.</font>

1391
01:59:51,292 --> 01:59:53,915
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't run around
with guns on me.</font>

1392
01:59:53,949 --> 01:59:56,573
<font face="Comic Sans MS">This is, this is crazy.</font>

1393
01:59:56,607 --> 01:59:58,402
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Sit yourself down, Jack.</font>

1394
02:00:11,898 --> 02:00:13,590
<font face="Comic Sans MS">This is S.P.</font>

1395
02:00:15,454 --> 02:00:17,111
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I wanna get ahold of Rob.</font>

1396
02:00:22,944 --> 02:00:24,877
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, when you get hold of him,
you'll tell him</font>

1397
02:00:24,911 --> 02:00:26,879
<font face="Comic Sans MS">to get over here straight away.</font>

1398
02:00:28,777 --> 02:00:30,572
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I've caught Jack.</font>

1399
02:00:38,891 --> 02:00:41,135
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm kind of glad that you are
the one that caught me.</font>

1400
02:00:45,553 --> 02:00:47,382
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Perhaps you don't know this..</font>

1401
02:00:49,591 --> 02:00:51,973
<font face="Comic Sans MS">...but I think of you
as my best friend.</font>

1402
02:00:55,942 --> 02:00:58,290
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Now that might not be
a big deal to you..</font>

1403
02:01:00,154 --> 02:01:03,467
<font face="Comic Sans MS">...but you've meant
a great deal to me.</font>

1404
02:01:07,506 --> 02:01:10,612
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It feels quite nice
knowing that it's all over.</font>

1405
02:01:17,688 --> 02:01:20,208
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Somebody had to free me</font>

1406
02:01:20,243 --> 02:01:24,661
<font face="Comic Sans MS">and stop me from stealing things
that don't belong to me.</font>

1407
02:01:26,421 --> 02:01:29,424
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And that someone
turned out to be you.</font>

1408
02:01:31,185 --> 02:01:35,430
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Do you remember the time you
took down that 8 pointer</font>

1409
02:01:35,465 --> 02:01:37,501
<font face="Comic Sans MS">that I'd been tracking
for 4 days?</font>

1410
02:01:40,608 --> 02:01:43,611
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It was on my territory
for sure.</font>

1411
02:01:43,645 --> 02:01:45,854
<font face="Comic Sans MS">No one's questioning that.</font>

1412
02:01:45,889 --> 02:01:47,615
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You've always been
a great shot.</font>

1413
02:01:49,272 --> 02:01:52,861
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Now would you, uh,
quit pointing that gun at me?</font>

1414
02:01:54,277 --> 02:01:56,244
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Kind of hurting my feelings
a little bit.</font>

1415
02:01:58,591 --> 02:02:00,421
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm not going anywhere.</font>

1416
02:02:02,146 --> 02:02:04,114
<font face="Comic Sans MS">After all you know me, S.P.</font>

1417
02:02:09,982 --> 02:02:10,982
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah.</font>

1418
02:02:12,536 --> 02:02:13,848
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I know you.</font>

1419
02:02:17,300 --> 02:02:19,716
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And you've never lied to me.</font>

1420
02:02:20,510 --> 02:02:21,787
<font face="Comic Sans MS">No.</font>

1421
02:02:31,659 --> 02:02:34,869
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Just as fast
as I always was, huh?</font>

1422
02:02:37,043 --> 02:02:39,045
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You wouldn't make it
to the door.</font>

1423
02:02:45,259 --> 02:02:46,708
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What have I done?</font>

1424
02:04:23,799 --> 02:04:25,076
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You got him, S.P.</font>

1425
02:04:27,078 --> 02:04:29,426
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, I'll take it from here.</font>

1426
02:05:10,398 --> 02:05:11,951
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Can we agree on this?</font>

1427
02:05:13,711 --> 02:05:15,886
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Is that a full metal jacket
cartridge?</font>

1428
02:05:19,061 --> 02:05:21,823
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes, sir. That is..</font>

1429
02:05:21,857 --> 02:05:24,826
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That is a full metal jacket
rifle cartridge.</font>

1430
02:05:24,860 --> 02:05:26,241
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, please, please</font>

1431
02:05:26,275 --> 02:05:28,208
<font face="Comic Sans MS">please, don't do this, please.</font>

1432
02:05:28,243 --> 02:05:30,763
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Alright, come on.
- Don't do it, please!</font>

1433
02:06:21,192 --> 02:06:22,400
<font face="Comic Sans MS">No, no.</font>

1434
02:06:23,540 --> 02:06:24,851
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I can't focus.</font>

1435
02:06:25,680 --> 02:06:27,129
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It's too close.</font>

1436
02:08:32,323 --> 02:08:33,531
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Perfect.</font>

1437
02:08:40,159 --> 02:08:41,470
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Jack!</font>

1438
02:08:49,306 --> 02:08:50,687
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Jack!</font>

1439
02:09:11,708 --> 02:09:12,778
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Who are you?</font>

1440
02:09:13,675 --> 02:09:15,090
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Call me Verge.</font>

1441
02:09:21,545 --> 02:09:23,340
<font face="Comic Sans MS">How did you get in here?</font>

1442
02:09:26,446 --> 02:09:27,655
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What do you want?</font>

1443
02:09:28,725 --> 02:09:31,313
<font face="Comic Sans MS">As I see it,
it's you who called me.</font>

1444
02:09:39,839 --> 02:09:43,774
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I've been with you for a while,
you just didn't notice me.</font>

1445
02:09:59,997 --> 02:10:03,138
<font face="Comic Sans MS">So, did you come here
to stop me?</font>

1446
02:10:05,693 --> 02:10:08,350
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I haven't come here to stop you
from anything.</font>

1447
02:10:08,385 --> 02:10:10,836
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I just have one question.</font>

1448
02:10:13,562 --> 02:10:16,117
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What's the question?</font>

1449
02:10:16,151 --> 02:10:19,810
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Wasn't there something about
you building a house?</font>

1450
02:10:22,019 --> 02:10:24,884
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Wasn't Jack going to
build a house?</font>

1451
02:10:33,582 --> 02:10:34,791
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes.</font>

1452
02:10:37,034 --> 02:10:40,106
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I... I... I was..</font>

1453
02:10:44,801 --> 02:10:46,043
<font face="Comic Sans MS">...trying..</font>

1454
02:10:47,217 --> 02:10:49,081
<font face="Comic Sans MS">...but I didn't get very far.</font>

1455
02:11:05,200 --> 02:11:06,546
<font face="Comic Sans MS">This is the police.</font>

1456
02:11:06,581 --> 02:11:09,308
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Come out with your hands
where we can see them</font>

1457
02:11:14,934 --> 02:11:17,626
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I can see it's going to be
a bit difficult</font>

1458
02:11:17,661 --> 02:11:20,698
<font face="Comic Sans MS">to get that house built,
but perhaps another one.</font>

1459
02:11:24,219 --> 02:11:27,119
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Think, Jack, after all
you are an engineer</font>

1460
02:11:27,153 --> 02:11:29,224
<font face="Comic Sans MS">and call yourself an architect.</font>

1461
02:11:36,162 --> 02:11:38,509
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I've been told you have an
interesting theory</font>

1462
02:11:38,544 --> 02:11:41,789
<font face="Comic Sans MS">about the material</font>

1463
02:11:41,823 --> 02:11:45,206
<font face="Comic Sans MS">which you claim
has its own will.</font>

1464
02:11:45,240 --> 02:11:48,209
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Find the material, Jack</font>

1465
02:11:48,243 --> 02:11:50,211
<font face="Comic Sans MS">and let it do the work.</font>

1466
02:12:43,574 --> 02:12:45,922
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Your house is a fine little
house, Jack.</font>

1467
02:12:49,270 --> 02:12:51,065
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It's absolutely usable.</font>

1468
02:13:09,255 --> 02:13:10,878
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Are you coming, Jack?</font>

1469
02:13:58,995 --> 02:14:02,895
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm here... Jack.</font>

1470
02:14:11,007 --> 02:14:13,181
<font face="Comic Sans MS">May I ask you something?</font>

1471
02:14:13,216 --> 02:14:15,494
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I can't promise I'll answer.</font>

1472
02:14:16,944 --> 02:14:19,705
<font face="Comic Sans MS">R... right,
that is exactly what I meant.</font>

1473
02:14:21,051 --> 02:14:23,812
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Um, are you allowed to speak
along the way?</font>

1474
02:14:25,124 --> 02:14:27,368
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I was thinking
there might be rules.</font>

1475
02:14:28,541 --> 02:14:29,991
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Put it this way</font>

1476
02:14:30,026 --> 02:14:33,857
<font face="Comic Sans MS">very few make it all the way
without uttering a word.</font>

1477
02:14:33,891 --> 02:14:36,101
<font face="Comic Sans MS">People are overcome
with a strange</font>

1478
02:14:36,135 --> 02:14:39,483
<font face="Comic Sans MS">and sudden need
to confess on these trips.</font>

1479
02:14:39,518 --> 02:14:41,382
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And not all of it can be said</font>

1480
02:14:41,416 --> 02:14:45,006
<font face="Comic Sans MS">to be of great
rhetorical quality</font>

1481
02:14:45,041 --> 02:14:46,870
<font face="Comic Sans MS">but do carry on merrily</font>

1482
02:14:46,904 --> 02:14:49,597
<font face="Comic Sans MS">just don't believe you're
going to tell me something</font>

1483
02:14:49,631 --> 02:14:51,564
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I haven't heard before.</font>

1484
02:16:29,835 --> 02:16:31,630
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Do you hear a buzzing sound?</font>

1485
02:16:31,664 --> 02:16:32,664
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes.</font>

1486
02:16:33,804 --> 02:16:35,841
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And I don't think
you want to know</font>

1487
02:16:35,875 --> 02:16:37,636
<font face="Comic Sans MS">where it's coming from.</font>

1488
02:16:41,502 --> 02:16:43,090
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I wanna know everything.</font>

1489
02:16:44,815 --> 02:16:47,163
<font face="Comic Sans MS">For thousands of years
human beings</font>

1490
02:16:47,197 --> 02:16:50,062
<font face="Comic Sans MS">have tried to localize hell.</font>

1491
02:16:50,097 --> 02:16:51,443
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Among other methods</font>

1492
02:16:51,477 --> 02:16:55,309
<font face="Comic Sans MS">by seeking the sound
it generates.</font>

1493
02:16:55,343 --> 02:16:59,968
<font face="Comic Sans MS">One shouldn't focus on
extracting screams and wailing</font>

1494
02:17:00,003 --> 02:17:03,179
<font face="Comic Sans MS">because the cries of pain
of so many millions</font>

1495
02:17:03,213 --> 02:17:05,664
<font face="Comic Sans MS">of individuals together..</font>

1496
02:17:07,666 --> 02:17:10,117
<font face="Comic Sans MS">...becomes what you have
just heard.</font>

1497
02:17:10,151 --> 02:17:13,016
<font face="Comic Sans MS">A buzzing sound whose intensity</font>

1498
02:17:13,050 --> 02:17:15,777
<font face="Comic Sans MS">will increase
as we get ever closer</font>

1499
02:17:15,812 --> 02:17:18,090
<font face="Comic Sans MS">to the presence of suffering.</font>

1500
02:18:49,975 --> 02:18:51,356
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Verge?</font>

1501
02:18:51,390 --> 02:18:53,185
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm here, Jack.</font>

1502
02:19:03,782 --> 02:19:05,784
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't feel so good, Verge.</font>

1503
02:19:09,857 --> 02:19:11,790
<font face="Comic Sans MS">There's a sour taste
in my mouth.</font>

1504
02:19:13,170 --> 02:19:16,726
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You want me to show you the way
to the next whiskey bar?</font>

1505
02:20:56,826 --> 02:20:59,346
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Those are the Elysian Fields.</font>

1506
02:21:02,901 --> 02:21:04,799
<font face="Comic Sans MS">We don't have access here.</font>

1507
02:23:07,163 --> 02:23:10,338
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That's how deep
the deepest hell goes.</font>

1508
02:23:17,967 --> 02:23:21,004
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It's actually not here
I'm to deliver you..</font>

1509
02:23:22,799 --> 02:23:25,215
<font face="Comic Sans MS">...however improbable
that may sound..</font>

1510
02:23:26,389 --> 02:23:28,598
<font face="Comic Sans MS">...but a couple of circles
higher up.</font>

1511
02:23:36,261 --> 02:23:39,022
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I took you down here
as a kind of a favor..</font>

1512
02:23:40,541 --> 02:23:44,649
<font face="Comic Sans MS">...because you did after all
give me a little to chew on</font>

1513
02:23:44,683 --> 02:23:46,996
<font face="Comic Sans MS">with your story,
and I understood</font>

1514
02:23:47,030 --> 02:23:49,239
<font face="Comic Sans MS">that you wanted to see it all.</font>

1515
02:24:05,290 --> 02:24:09,018
<font face="Comic Sans MS">When you are done looking,
we'll turn back.</font>

1516
02:24:13,954 --> 02:24:15,818
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Where does that path lead?</font>

1517
02:24:16,853 --> 02:24:18,303
<font face="Comic Sans MS">On the other side.</font>

1518
02:24:20,650 --> 02:24:25,206
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It leads out of hell and up.</font>

1519
02:24:27,795 --> 02:24:31,281
<font face="Comic Sans MS">As you can see
there was once a bridge</font>

1520
02:24:31,316 --> 02:24:33,352
<font face="Comic Sans MS">but that was before my time.</font>

1521
02:24:42,189 --> 02:24:45,606
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Isn't it possible
to climb all the way around?</font>

1522
02:24:49,576 --> 02:24:50,887
<font face="Comic Sans MS">This way..</font>

1523
02:24:52,268 --> 02:24:54,235
<font face="Comic Sans MS">...and make it over
to the other side?</font>

1524
02:24:56,652 --> 02:25:00,172
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Quite a few have tried,
but I have to say..</font>

